Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:01.15,Text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn方正中雅宋_GBK\b1\fs70\c&HBE8E79&\bord5\3c&HF9FCFC&}记者{\fs110} 千田奈留
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.10,Explain,,0,0,0,,妻子都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.10,Explain,,0,0,0,,你却在画鸡*吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.10,Explain,,0,0,0,,真够恶心的——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.35,Explain,,0,0,0,,这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.35,Explain,,0,0,0,,睾快点（）真是放肆！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.35,Explain,,0,0,0,,荤段子搞得风生水起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.35,Explain,,0,0,0,,这人已经完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.85,Explain,,0,0,0,,这家伙的漫画我已经笑不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.57,Explain,,0,0,0,,这里有秘密
